    "The GAT technique focuses on extracting more significant information from first-order neighbors.",
    "In this section, we conduct experiments on multiple benchmark networks to assess the effectiveness of the proposed solution.",
    "We employ visualization and analysis techniques to showcase the efficacy of our suggested framework based on experimental findings.",
    "In addition, we perform ablation experiments to emphasize the necessity of collecting complex interactions and hidden information within the network.",
    "In order to assess the significance of higher-order information and complex interactions, we performed a series of experiments on two extensively utilized network datasets in the domain of graph representation learning."
